Class RulePerformanceEvaluator.CriterionClassWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • adaa.analytics.rules.operator.RulePerformanceEvaluator.CriterionClassWrapper
  • Enclosing class:
    RulePerformanceEvaluator

    protected static class RulePerformanceEvaluator.CriterionClassWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper for performance criteria classes. Allows uniform handling of different criteria classes - a class may represent a single criterion, or several of them (this requires specifying additional integer parameter).
